Fire Hydrants, Fire Hydrants Collected Upon Installation, Published In 2010, 1:600 (1In=50Ft) Scale, Columbia County Board Of Commissioners.

This Fire Hydrants dataset, published at 1:600 (1in=50ft) scale, was produced all or in part from Field Survey/GPS information as of 2010. It is described as 'Fire Hydrants collected upon installation'. Data by this publisher are often provided in State Plane coordinate system; in a Transverse Mercator projection; The extent of these data is generally Columbia County, GA,Grovetown, GA,Harlem, GA. This starter metadata was auto-generated through the Ramona GIS Inventory System (www.gisinventory.net) and does not represent all information about this data set.
